headline: Fallen Angels Outperform Again In Q3 Amid Fed Cut And Trade Noise
summary: Fallen angels outperformed the broad high yield market by 0.59% in Q3 (2.99% vs. 2.40%), widening the year-to-date gap to 0.78% (7.84% vs. 7.06%).
